# Template:
# Change a quadratic function from standard form to vertex form. 
# Fractions are involved.
#
#       f(x) = x^2 + ax + b
#
# a is even.
#
# Last updated: Carl Yao, 11/13/2014
# ENDDESCRIPTION

## DBCCSS('A-REI.4.b')
## DBsubject('Algebra')
